                <mxCell id="cnt-001" value="&lt;b&gt;CRA UI&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#d0e8ff&quot;&gt;[Web Application — CNT-001]&lt;br&gt;[CRC Platform / Technology: TBD]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font&gt;CRC Assessment Interface. Captures Business Activity rating (only manual input), qualitative L2/L1 ratings, rationale, and all conclusion fields. Surfaces publication ratings and validate counter to Preparer. Hosts Approver review workflow.&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#1168BD;strokeColor=#0E5AA0;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontColor=#ffffff;align=left;spacingLeft=8;verticalAlign=top;" parent="1" vertex="1">
