                <mxCell id="cnt-002" value="&lt;b&gt;CRA Rating Results Service&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#d0e8ff&quot;&gt;[API Service — CNT-002]&lt;br&gt;[Internal Microservice / Technology: TBD]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font&gt;Core calculation engine. Computes 100% systemic publication-level IR and CE ratings. Applies Preparer qualitative L2/L1 overrides. Runs GRC Residual Risk Matrix lookup. Enforces mandatory-field validation gate before submission.&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#1168BD;strokeColor=#0E5AA0;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontColor=#ffffff;align=left;spacingLeft=8;verticalAlign=top;" parent="1" vertex="1">
