                <mxCell id="cnt-005" value="&lt;b&gt;Third-Party Dashboard&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#d0e8ff&quot;&gt;[Web Application — CNT-005]&lt;br&gt;[Separate Microservice — Independent Daily Refresh]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font&gt;Searchable third-party risk profiles per GAU. Operates fully independently from the annual CRA snapshot pipeline. Refreshes daily from MCA. Accessible via Aggregation tab in CRC module.&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#1168BD;strokeColor=#0E5AA0;strokeWidth=2;strokeDasharray=8 4;fontSize=12;fontColor=#ffffff;align=left;spacingLeft=8;verticalAlign=top;dashed=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
